    "body": "`setup-env.sh` was not properly detecting a bash shell when bash was run as `/bin/sh`.\r\n\r\nThis fixes the detection routine to always report `bash` when `bash` is run as `sh`.  We no longer parse the path to the executable indicated in `$BASH`.\r\n\r\n@wspear -- this should fix your issue.",
